Hey @markkhoffmann -- thanks for reaching out! Yeah, we'd love to speak. Benefits really depend on circumstance, but a lot has to do with re-thinking how data is shared, versus replacing data infrastructure within a single company's database.
What have you guys seen as some of the major benefits of the process besides not having to worry about trust issues of a centralized single company's database and unwanted tampering of data?
@danielmason1 was looking at @elemetric_ and was curious to pick your brain on the benefits of putting data on a Blockchain outside of currencies
